cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper deals with active visual exploration, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of spatial memory maps and the emphasis on the advantages of retina-like glimpses suggest that the paper may also fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE).
